ring Boot application\n- Added @SpringBootApplication annotation\n- Added @ComponentScan for package scanning\n- Added @EntityScan to specify JPA entity location\n- Added @EnableTransactionManagement for transaction support\n- Note: @EnableJpaRepositories import is present but annotation not used (can be added if needed)\n- Implemented main method to run SpringApplication\n\nThe migration configuration is now complete and ready for further code conversion from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1968c9d1-9222-41bb-9d6c-3e0081e3cb16","uuid":"e16b3330-5915-4f3f-95d8-6a46ab18f64b"}
