{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_016aTE4wwBBYV5XGmfaqr9zt","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All the changes have been successfully applied. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\nAll ObjectMapper qualifiers have been successfully fixed in the four Spring controller files. The changes ensure that controllers using `@JsonRootName` annotated response classes (like `UserResponse`, `ArticleResponse`, `ProfileResponse`, `CommentResponse`) now inject the correct `wrapRootValueObjectMapper` to produce properly wrapped JSON responses like `{\"user\":{...}}`.\n\n### 1. ArticlesResource.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Added `@Qualifier(\"wrapRootValueObjectMapper\")` to the `objectMapper` parameter in the constructor (line 59)\n- Removed unused import `import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.qualifiers.NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper;`\n- The `noWrapObjectMapper` parameter already had the correct qualifier and remains unchanged\n\n### 2. UsersResource.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Added import: `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;` (line 6)\n- Added `@Qualifier(\"wrapRootValueObjectMapper\")` to the `objectMapper` parameter in the constructor (line 36)\n\n### 3. UserResource.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Added import: `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;` (line 6)\n- Added `@Qualifier(\"wrapRootValueObjectMapper\")` to the `objectMapper` parameter in the constructor (line 33)\n\n### 4. ProfilesResource.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Added import: `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;` (line 6)\n- Added `@Qualifier(\"wrapRootValueObjectMapper\")` to the `objectMapper` parameter in the constructor (line 32)\n\nAll controllers will now correctly inject the `wrapRootValueObjectMapper` bean, which is configured to serialize responses with root value wrapping, producing the expected JSON format for responses with `@JsonRootName` annotations."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1968c9d1-9222-41bb-9d6c-3e0081e3cb16","uuid":"e6e5dca9-e86f-46a1-9740-e499322bb94f"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VEwQWdDa6pZJzhL3pJEALn","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All obsolete files and directories have been successfully removed. Here's a summary of what was deleted:\n\n## Deleted Files Summary\n\n### 1. Old JAX-RS Security Files (4 files)\nThese were replaced by Spring HandlerInterceptor + @Authenticated:\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/annotation/Secured.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/context/DecodedJWTSecurityContext.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/context/EmptySecurityContext.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/filter/AuthorizationFilter.java`\n\n### 2. Old JAX-RS ExceptionMapper Files (3 files)\nThese were replaced by GlobalExceptionHandler:\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BusinessExceptionMapper.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java`\n\n### 3. Old CDI Qualifier (1 file)\nThis was replaced by Spring @Qualifier:\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/qualifiers/NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper.java`\n\n### 4. Old Liberty/Jakarta EE Config Files (5 files)\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/beans.xml`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/microprofile-config.properties`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/test/resources/META-INF/beans.xml`\n\n### 5. Removed Empty Directories (3 directories)\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/context/`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/qualifiers/`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/liberty/`