ion \"tag_relationship\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.905Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.905Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"articles\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.905Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.905Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"comments\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.906Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.906Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"favorite_relationship\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.906Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.906Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"follow_relationship\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.907Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.907Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"tag_relationship\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.907Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.907Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"tags\" does not exist, skipping\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.908Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : SQL Warning Code: 0, SQLState: 00000\n2026-03-14T06:09:39.908Z  WARN 1 --- [           main] o.h.engine.jdbc.spi.SqlExceptionHelper   : table \"users