{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01JWLfn7nSEWB4K67544B8KA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished in this session (continuing from the previous context):\n\n## Migration Complete\n\nThe Jakarta EE (MicroProfile/OpenLiberty) to Spring Boot 3.2.5 migration is fully done.\n\n### What was completed in this session:\n\n1. **Fixed ObjectMapper qualifiers** - All 4 controllers (`ArticlesResource`, `UsersResource`, `UserResource`, `ProfilesResource`) were updated to inject `@Qualifier(\"wrapRootValueObjectMapper\")` so that responses with `@JsonRootName` annotations produce correct wrapped JSON (e.g., `{\"user\":{...}}`).\n\n2. **Deleted 13 obsolete files** - Removed old JAX-RS security files (`Secured.java`, `DecodedJWTSecurityContext`, `EmptySecurityContext`, `AuthorizationFilter`), old exception mappers, CDI qualifier, Liberty config files (`server.xml`, `persistence.xml`, `beans.xml`, `microprofile-config.properties`), and old MicroShed test files.\n\n3. **Updated start.sh** - Changed from `mvn clean liberty:run` to `mvn clean package -DskipTests && java -jar target/realworld-spring-1.0.0.jar`.\n\n4. **Created smoke.py** - 19 comprehensive smoke tests covering all API endpoints.\n\n5. **Built Docker image and ran container** - Application starts successfully on Spring Boot with embedded Tomcat.\n\n6. **All 19 smoke tests passed** - Tags, user CRUD, authentication, profiles, follow/unfollow, articles CRUD, comments, favorites, and unauthorized access validation all working correctly.\n\n7. **Documented everything in CHANGELOG.md**."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":349,"cache_read_input_tokens":83527,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":349,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":404},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1